      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "第一回！　franさんの漫画会議～！\n今回から、遙子さんも参加してくれますわ！",
      "startTime": 5.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 8.3711341857
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "は～い！　franさんの企画をお手伝いに来た\n佐伯遙子、十七歳ですっ。イラストなら任せてね",
      "startTime": 13.0378008524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "優は残念ながら予定が重なっていて、参加出来ないそう\nですが、これから三人で頑張っていきますわよ～！",
      "startTime": 23.5000001907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 24.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 28.0429254531
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "結局、漫画家の先生が見つからなくて自分で描くことに\nなったけど……アシスタントがこの二人で大丈夫かしら",
      "startTime": 32.8666667302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 38.5335151671
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "まぁとりあえず、本題に入るけど\nこれから私達三人で協力して、漫画を描くことになるわ",
      "startTime": 41.4666667302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 46.1662590978
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "さっき絵を見せたけど、主要なキャラはあんな感じの\nタッチで、よほどのことがない限り私が描くつもりよ",
      "startTime": 49.6333336512,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "手伝ってくれるっていうなら、すずは背景担当、遙子は\nベタ塗りやトーン、あとはモブキャラを描いてくれる？",
      "startTime": 59.3333354313,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 63.541497707
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、頑張るわ\nfranさんとお仕事が出来る日が来るなんてね",
      "startTime": 66.2081643737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 69.9081658996
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "franさんの絵も、かなり上達してましたわね\nこの短期間で凄いですわ",
      "startTime": 73.4333356857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 75.922950331
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "これくらい当然よ\nこの前は、漫画のタッチに慣れてなかっただけだし",
      "startTime": 78.066669019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 81.7117258704
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "今回は、そんな絵に見合うだけのお話を考えないとね\n二人は、どんなストーリーがいいと思う？",
      "startTime": 86.566669019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 89.4185965216
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "はいはーい！　遙子、思いつきました！\n漫画の王道、学園ラブストーリーなんてどうかしら",
      "startTime": 93.6852631882,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9566.6666667,
          "startTime": 103.2519298549
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11233.333333399998,
          "startTime": 104.9185965216
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12900.000000000005,
          "startTime": 106.5852631882
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14564.736811800003,
          "startTime": 108.25
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 15914.770145100007,
          "startTime": 109.6000333333
